; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;<br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;由中国纺织工业联合会的“纺织之光”科技基金会、中国纺织服装教育学会共同主持的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">2016</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">“</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">纺织之光</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">”</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">教师奖、学生奖评审会于</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">9</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">26</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">日在江南大学举行，参加会议的有来自全国</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">15</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">所有代表性的纺织院校或纺织学科的教授、人事处及学生处<br> 的领导，我校与清华大学、江南大学是第五次参加。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">\n  <o:p></o:p></span></p> \n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 115%; text-autospace: ; text-indent: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">本年度评审会主要进行了以下工作：（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">1</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">）根据“关于推荐纺织之光奖教金和奖学金候选人的通知”（中纺教</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast">[2016]62</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast">号</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">）要求，认真审阅了各校</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">“</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">纺织之光</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">”</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">师生</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">奖选拔、推荐候选人的申报材料及事迹，在充分讨论的基础上，确认获奖名单，并在各校候选人中最后评定出本年度</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">1</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">名教师特别奖、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">2</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">名学生特别奖的获奖人；（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">2</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">）商讨如何更好开展纺织科技教育基金会的工作；（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">3</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">）交流了各校在师资培养、人才引进、教学改革、管理机制等方面的经验和体会；（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">4</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">）</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 115%; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 黑体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-fareast">开展“纺织之光”爱益行联合公益计划，支持重庆贫困地区“钱之光希望小学”办学</span><span style="font-siz